OUR MISSION:
To be a gathering place for our community, serving delicious coffee and food while making each customer’s day better by our kindness, caring, and love. To become intricately woven into the heart and very fabric of our community, always seeking ways to become involved with and serve the community itself.
T396
Local Arts: Lending our stage to musicians, poets, artists and authors
Local Charities: Donating of product, finances, and our time
Global Communities: Purchasing Direct Trade coffees and Fair Trade Teas that provide living wages to farmers around the globe
